Staying in this property is not for those who seek luxury at each turn.	Because of abnormally warm temperatures, the air conditioning in the room was true luxury.	Moreover, the maid's hair was on my sheets, and i seriously doubted the integrity and cleanliness of the mattresses and sheets.	Try to remember where you deposited the bike and its number in case of challenges.	You really feel on vacation sitting at the cafe table on your balcony eating croissants for breakfast.	After a few disconcerting minutes getting used to traveling at the speed of bike in the city of lights we were comfortable.	Truly we were delighted with our find here, and will be booking here again for sure.